"     Deputy Editor",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?39/18/40233/contributors\">",
"     James F Wiley, II, MD, MPH",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
